    <briefdescription>
<para>Structure to encapsulate a possible set of streams configuration. Such set describes a possible way of setting #stream_configs in <ref refid="struct_m_l_depth_camera_settings" kindref="compound">MLDepthCameraSettings</ref> and may hold multiple <ref refid="struct_m_l_depth_camera_stream_capability" kindref="compound">MLDepthCameraStreamCapability</ref> for different streams. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Whole <ref refid="struct_m_l_depth_camera_capability_1ad3cce8a574c3b11eecf0b32dcad57d7e" kindref="member">stream_capabilities</ref> array describe a single configuration. Using only part of it is not recommended.</para>
<para>The capabilities supported by the depth camera can be queried with <ref refid="group___d_cam_1gaf68bfbf8b5b1bcee305f026a7de4db6d" kindref="member">MLDepthCameraGetCapabilities()</ref>.</para>
